### Test Start

STEP
Verify correct URL
	(https://test.fast.weown.com/own/platform)
Verify START page is visible, visibility of buttons:
	buttonVisitOurSite
	buttonLogin
	buttonRegister
	buttonFacebook
	buttonGoogle
EXPECTED RESULT
	URL is correct
	All elements are shown on page
	Buttons are correctly aligned

STEP
Verify START page resizing:
	using mouse resize the browser window
EXPECTED RESULT
	Buttons are on place.
	Structure is not changed



### Test Register

STEP
Verify correct URL
	(https://test.fast.weown.com/own/platform)
Verify START page is visible, visibility of buttons:
	buttonVisitOurSite
	buttonLogin
	buttonRegister
	buttonFacebook
	buttonGoogle
EXPECTED RESULT
	All elements are shown on page
	Buttons are correctly aligned

STEP
Verify REGISTER page is visible, visibility of buttons, links and inputs:
	buttonIcon
	linkTokenizeYourBusiness
	inputUsername
	inputPassword
	buttonNextStep
EXPECTED RESULT
	All elements are shown on page
	Buttons and inputs are correctly aligned

STEP
Verify REGISTER page look:
	input fields are aligned
	login button is bellow input fields
EXPECTED RESULT
	All elements are shown on page
	Buttons and inputs are correctly aligned

STEP
Verify REGISTER page resizing:
	buttons are on place
	structure is not changed
EXPECTED RESULT
	Buttons are on place.
	Structure is not changed

STEP
Verify REGISTER page process:
	Username/Password page
EXPECTED RESULT
	buttonNextStep is not working if input fields are empty.
	"This field is required." error is shown.
	If "First/Last name" is missing pink popup window opens with message:
	"Oops, that didn't work
	The first/last name field is required"

STEP
Verify REGISTER page process:
	Setup Your Profile is visible with:
	inputBusinessName
	inputCountryOfIncorporation
	checkButtonConfirm
	buttonPrevious
	buttonNext
EXPECTED RESULT
	If "Business Name / Country" is missing pink popup window opens with message:
	"Oops, that didn't work
	The BusinessName/Country name field is required"

STEP
Verify REGISTER page process:
	Enter your email address is visible with:
	inputEmail
	buttonPrevious
	buttonNext
EXPECTED RESULT
	Verify email input control is working.
	Input has to be in em@il.com format
	Until input is correct buttonNextStep is deactivated.

STEP
Verify REGISTER page process:
	Enter your password page is visible with:
	inputPassword
	inputConfirmPassword
	checkButtonCaptcha
	checkButtonAcceptTerms
	buttonPrevious
	buttonNext
EXPECTED RESULT
	Verify password input control is working.
	Input has to be in abcABC123!@# format
	Until input is correct buttonNextStep is deactivated.

STEP
Verify REGISTER page process:
	Let's create your asset page is visible with:
	inputAssetName
	inputAssetSymbol
	inputTotalAssetSupply
	checkButtonUseAsset
	buttonPrevious
	buttonNext
EXPECTED RESULT
	Verify asset symbol input control is working.
	Input has to be 3-13 uppercase letters and numbers only
	Until input is correct buttonFinish is deactivated.

STEP
Verify REGISTER page success:
	buttonGetStarted is visible and click able
EXPECTED RESULT
	Comment is written:
	All done! 
	You've created your business profile
	Hit the button below to start creating investment offers.



